/> | %iænǧæl%i ‘надежда’.</etym><etym xml:lang="en">It literally means “bad hope”; see %r3%r<ref type="xr" target="#entry_fyd"/> | %ifud%i ‘bad’ and <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ænqælyn"/> | %iænǧælun%i ‘hope’, ‘count on’, <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ænqæl"/> | %iænǧæl%i ‘hope’.</etym></entry></body></text></TEI>